Author: 100percentthatED
Text: Oh ya I have a specialist and my husband is fully aware of my inner bologna. Unfortunately, it doesn't make me any less crazy. Ugh

Author: tea-addicted-taemint
Text: I know the feeling. I've been struggling for 7 years with periods of active relapse and recovery in that time. If it's possible, I would recommend seeing a professional or at least talking to your husband about what's going on.
